lead_paragraph: Insisting "everyone needs money," Pele took a lingering look at a lifetime of medals, trinkets and memorabilia that auctioneers hope will generate around $7 million.

headline.print_headline: 'Everybody Needs Money': Pele Cashes In on Memorabilia
